    </div>
    <ul class="fe-cat-notes">
      <li><Icon name="visibility" class="fe-material" /> Offer a show-password toggle; <strong>never block paste</strong>.</li>
      <li><Icon name="accessibility_new" class="fe-material" /> Use <code>new-password</code> on sign-up so managers offer a strong one.</li>
